		<title>We’ll Work Hard For National Growth And Development</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="/index.php/past-speeches/economics/68-we-ll-work-hard-for-national-growth-and-development"/>
		<published>2022-06-11T15:50:12+00:00</published>
		<updated>2022-06-11T15:50:12+00:00</updated>
		<id>/index.php/past-speeches/economics/68-we-ll-work-hard-for-national-growth-and-development</id>
		<author>
			<name>Super User</name>
			<email>tunde.obadina@afbis.com</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remarks by Senator (Dr.) Abdullahi Adamu, CON, (Turakin Keffi) Chairman, All Progressives Congress on the Occasion of Conferment of National Productivity Order of Merit, State House Banquet Hall, Abuja, Thursday, 12th May, 2022&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;On behalf of all the awardees, I have the honour and privilege to express our gratitude to Mr. President, Commander-in-Chief for considering us worthy of the National Productivity Order of Merit award.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Mr. President, the awardees have asked me to extol your leadership qualities which have made us, and indeed all citizens of this great country to commit themselves to national growth and development. We are all inspired when we note that through your leadership, all indices of development in the past six years have continued to move in the positive direction in spite of global disruptions.&lt;/p&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remarks by Senator (Dr.) Abdullahi Adamu, CON, (Turakin Keffi) Chairman, All Progressives Congress on the Occasion of Conferment of National Productivity Order of Merit, State House Banquet Hall, Abuja, Thursday, 12th May, 2022&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;On behalf of all the awardees, I have the honour and privilege to express our gratitude to Mr. President, Commander-in-Chief for considering us worthy of the National Productivity Order of Merit award.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Mr. President, the awardees have asked me to extol your leadership qualities which have made us, and indeed all citizens of this great country to commit themselves to national growth and development. We are all inspired when we note that through your leadership, all indices of development in the past six years have continued to move in the positive direction in spite of global disruptions.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
